data.description: OWNER AGENT LISTING.THE COTTAGES AT BROW WOOD OFFERS A MAINTENANCE-FREE LIVING.  THIS HOME FEATURES 2 BR AND 2 FULL BATHS ON THE MAIN LEVEL AND A FULLY FURNISHED 3RD BEDROOM AND 3RD FULL BATHROOM IN THE UPSTAIRS BONUS ROOM.  THIS HOME IS AN ASHLEIGH FLOOR PLAN FEATURING AN OPEN CONCEPT SHOWCASING A LUXURIOUS KITCHEN WITH UPGRADED BERWYN QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS; 42'' LEVEL 3 UPPER SOFT CLOSE CABINETS THROUGHOUT IN GLACIER GRAY WITH CROWN MOLDING AND CLASSIC MATTE BLACK HARDWARE FOR PERFECT CONTRASTING ACCENT.  THIS KITCHEN BOASTS ALL STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES WITH A 5 BURNER GAS RANGE.  THE HOME FEATURES BEAUTIFULLY ENGINEERED 5'' HARDWOOD FLOORING HARDWOOD, CARPETED BEDROOMS AND BONUS AREA.  AS YOU ENTER INTO THE OWNERS SUITE, YOU WILL SEE VIEW A LARGE WALK-IN TILED SHOWER WITH AN UPGRADED FRAMELESS GLASS DOOR. NOTICE THE RAISED DOUBLE BOWL VANITY WITH GORGEOUS QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS COMPLETE WITH OIL RUBBED BRONZE HARDWARE  AND A SPACIOUS HARDWOOD FLOORED WALK-IN CLOSET,  ENJOY YOUR MORNING COFFEE FROM YOUR GATED, PRIVATE COURTYARD OR YOUR SUNSET FROM YOUR COVERED PORCH.  THIS HOME IS A MUST SEE.
